<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 18:14:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>流亡中国商人的幕僚长在美国承认欺诈罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/exiled-chinese-businessmans-chief-of-staff-pleads-guilty-us-fraud-2024-05-03/</link><description>流亡中国商人郭文贵的幕僚长周五承认与郭文贵合谋实施一项大规模计划，诈骗数千名投资者超过 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/exiled-chinese-businessmans-chief-of-staff-pleads-guilty-us-fraud-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大调查发现外国干预选举的证据，但结果不受影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-probe-finds-evidence-foreign-meddling-elections-results-not-affected-2024-05-03/</link><description>根据周五公布的初步调查结果，官方调查发现加拿大最近两次联邦选举有外国干预的证据，但投票结果没有受到影响，选举制度也很健全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-probe-finds-evidence-foreign-meddling-elections-results-not-affected-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称美国二次制裁旨在“遏制”中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-us-secondary-sanctions-aim-contain-china-2024-05-03/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部发言人玛丽亚·扎哈罗娃(Maria Zakharova)周五表示，美国正在利用对被视为与俄罗斯接触的中国企业实施二次制裁的威胁作为试图遏制北京的“借口”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 15:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-us-secondary-sanctions-aim-contain-china-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商赢得了在电动汽车税收抵免中使用中国石墨的延期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</link><description>美国财政部周五为汽车制造商提供了对来自中国的一些重要微量矿物（例如石墨）的电动汽车税收抵免的电池矿物要求的额外灵活性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>习近平访问之前，中国在法国电动汽车市场的份额下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</link><description>行业数据显示，法国政府减缓中国制造电动汽车涌入的努力正在取得成果，这突显了中国国家主席下周访问时最敏感的贸易问题之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟称三家中国电动汽车制造商提供的信息不足</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-information-three-chinese-ev-makers-insufficient-2024-05-03/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，欧盟委员会已警告三家中国电动汽车制造商，称他们没有为其反补贴调查提供足够的信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-information-three-chinese-ev-makers-insufficient-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>苹果股价上涨，创纪录的回购和销售增长预测吸引了投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-shares-jump-record-buyback-sales-growth-forecast-lure-investors-2024-05-03/</link><description>苹果股价周五上涨近 7%，这家 iPhone 制造商创纪录的股票回购计划和销售增长的承诺吸引了因担心中国需求疲软和竞争加剧而回避该股的投资者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-shares-jump-record-buyback-sales-growth-forecast-lure-investors-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>尽管价格下跌，但亚洲黄金消费大国印度和中国的黄金需求仍低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-demand-subdued-top-consumers-india-china-despite-price-drop-2024-05-03/</link><description>印度的实物黄金需求本周仍然低迷，尽管价格略有调整，因为买家等待更大的跌幅，而中国的溢价由于假期需求低迷而连续第二周下滑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:23:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-demand-subdued-top-consumers-india-china-despite-price-drop-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：乔布斯测试美联储的救济措施、苹果回购的冲击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国启动历史性月球背面采样任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/china-launches-historic-mission-retrieve-samples-far-side-moon-2024-05-03/</link><description>中国周五发射了一艘无人驾驶飞船，执行了近两个月的任务，从月球背面取回岩石和土壤，这是第一个进行如此雄心勃勃的尝试的国家。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 09:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/china-launches-historic-mission-retrieve-samples-far-side-moon-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国国防部长称，菲律宾在南海造成的损害是“不负责任的行为”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/damage-injury-philippines-south-china-sea-is-irresponsible-behaviour-says-us-2024-05-03/</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周四在谈到涉及中国的最新冲突时表示，在南海损坏菲律宾船只并造成船员受伤是无视国际法的“不负责任行为”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/damage-injury-philippines-south-china-sea-is-irresponsible-behaviour-says-us-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>瑞银表示全球对冲基金追逐港股反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-global-hedge-funds-chase-hong-kong-stocks-rally-ubs-says-2024-05-03/</link><description>瑞银集团在一份报告中表示，采用股票多空策略的全球对冲基金越来越看好中国，其购买香港上市股票的大幅增加就证明了这一点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-global-hedge-funds-chase-hong-kong-stocks-rally-ubs-says-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>股市上涨，收益率下跌，因希望美国劳动力紧张状况缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-03/</link><description>周五，华尔街跟随全球股市走高，此前有消息称上个月美国非农就业人数增长低于预期，缓解了投资者对紧张的劳动力市场和顽固的通胀不会让美联储很快降息的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:19:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>导弹防御在海湾和乌克兰的成功加剧了全球采购系统的紧迫性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/missile-defence-successes-gulf-ukraine-fuel-global-urgency-acquire-systems-2024-05-03/</link><description>专家表示，弹道导弹防御系统在以色列、红海和乌克兰首次面临复杂、高风险的战斗场景时取得成功，将鼓励全球军队投资昂贵的系统，并加剧导弹军备竞赛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/missile-defence-successes-gulf-ukraine-fuel-global-urgency-acquire-systems-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称中国飞机越过中线，中国进行着陆演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-14-chinese-military-planes-crossed-straits-median-line-2024-05-03/</link><description>台湾国防部周五表示，发现中国军机再次侵入敏感的台湾海峡，中国报道称其海军已使用登陆艇进行了战斗演习。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-14-chinese-military-planes-crossed-straits-median-line-2024-05-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>